  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Accountability and the Information Economy of Somalia &#x2013; Implementation Phase</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">BBC Media Action will harness the potential of the Somali media to hold national level government to account. As this implementation phase is based on intensive research conducted in Berbera, Somaliland, the primary focus will be on Somaliland (through working with Horn Cable TV and Radio Hargeisa) with a secondary focus on South Central and Puntland (reached by BBC Somali Service).</narrative>
